						<summary>

						<p>This registers an endowment (details not given) made by one Māyāṉ Perumāṉ of Pūñjiṟṟūr in Kiḻār-kūṟṟam for the daily feeding of five Brāhmaṇas in the <hi rend="italic">maṭha</hi> (attached to the temple) of Perumānaḍigaḷ at Govindapāḍi in Toṇḍai-nāḍu.</p>						

